{"tid":509002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"平安夜變失戀日 男生天台企跳","createTime":"2017-12-24T20:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T06:08:37.000Z","uid":122,"like":8,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5fb8edf35e407c838ace9ef05e2925ed787edaba","tid":509002,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T20:19:53.000Z","msg":"<strong>平安夜變失戀日 男生天台企跳</strong><br />\n<br />\n即時突發 <br />\n<br />\n2017-12-25 02:40:55 HKT<br />\n<br />\n油塘高翔苑高瑞閣天台，凌晨零時許，一名年輕大專生平安夜疑失戀，跑上大廈天台企圖跳樓，警方及消防員到場，將男子勸服拉回安全地方，由救護員送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，男生自小體弱多病，與新相識女友拍拖約半年，惟平安夜卻失戀，情緒低落跑上天台企圖自殺。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"a59ab0d9d2a41dfbf72bdc8dc6a7c238bc30c6ff","tid":509002,"uid":20522,"like":108,"dislike":2,"score":106,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T20:22:43.000Z","msg":"應該做咗半年兵諗住今日表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條女分分鐘同第二條仔扑緊嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e6ed0a3dc569c14f9d89758d0f2bf629bf24fb8","tid":509002,"uid":71725,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T22:41:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bf43ddd7459d0fe971d64e72ac4cad4da5c9526","tid":509002,"uid":40470,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T23:00:33.000Z","msg":"毒撚由終要扮跳樓先有人得閒理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<br />\n大專生？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff29c77f965758f9b65a945799a685b9f952ed7","tid":509002,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bf43ddd7459d0fe971d64e72ac4cad4da5c9526","tid":509002,"uid":40470,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-24T23:00:33.000Z","msg":"毒撚由終要扮跳樓先有人得閒理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" c